episodes.overview: Molly loses her streak with Celina and becomes jealous of Johanne and Celina's friendship and tries to get between them.

episodes.name: The pigeons are watching us!
episodes.overview: Can it be that the pigeons monitor the students at the school? Willum would not lie about such a strange theory - or would he?

episodes.name: In love with Nellie?
episodes.overview: Mia suddenly gets confused about her feelings for Adam and Nellie. Is she falling in love with someone else?

episodes.name: Willum's secret
episodes.overview: After moving, Willum keeps a secret, but can he keep it when the food club comes by?

episodes.name: Molly's chess dates
episodes.overview: Molly tells N.P. about her boy problems, but maybe her love is just right before her eyes? What will be Molly's next move?

episodes.name: The struggle for love
episodes.overview: Mia gives her and Adam one last chance, but is the battle for love already lost?

episodes.name: Melvin has to move
episodes.overview: Melvin's father tells them to move. Both Melvin and the whole class will be sad, but maybe it's not all bad ...

episodes.name: The most popular in the class
episodes.overview: Celina does not understand Liv's new popularity, but intends to be on Liv's side, but does Liv need Celina's support at all?

episodes.name: Robin says no
episodes.overview: 9th graders bully Robin, but Robin does not bother to find himself in it and decides to say no. Will Robin succeed in stopping them?

episodes.name: I Love You
episodes.overview: Johanne has found a bracelet for Jeppe that says I LOVE YOU. Is it cute or too much?

episodes.name: Is Michael fired?
episodes.overview: Why is Michael being called to Fromm's office? The class is afraid that Michael might be fired, but what can they do?

episodes.name: The class is saying goodbye
episodes.overview: Does the class lose Michael and why? The class puts all their love into saving the situation.

episodes.name: Burglary at school
episodes.overview: The new school year starts with chaos and drama, as there has been a burglary in the A class. Who could think of breaking into the school?

episodes.name: Who is the thief?
episodes.overview: Agnes and Bjarke have seen something suspicious at school. Have they uncovered the thief? And is it someone from the class who has stolen the money?

episodes.name: From friends to enemies
episodes.overview: Once Lotus and Agnes were best friends. Is Tobi the reason they are now enemies?

episodes.name: War against the new teacher
episodes.overview: The new class teacher gets a rough welcome. Do the class pranksters Lucca and Hugo manage to scare the new teacher away like they usually do?

episodes.name: Eigil loses a friend
episodes.overview: Noah is tired of Eigil skipping group work. But is there a serious reason for Eigil bailing on their project?

episodes.name: Møller's mysterious family
episodes.overview: Møller tells the class about his exotic lineage and becomes popular. However, Eske discovers that Møller's story may not be true?

episodes.name: Battle for Tobi
episodes.overview: Tobi and Lotus are best friends. However, the friendship is in jeopardy when Lotus goes berserk on Tobi's girlfriend, Clara. Can they stay friends?

episodes.name: Can Benja be trusted?
episodes.overview: Felix pressures Benja, who wants to prove that he is not a simp. Can Siri still trust Benja to keep her secret?

episodes.name: Eva is always alone
episodes.overview: Eva has no friends at school. Amalie decides to help, because who doesn't want to always be alone?

episodes.name: Future lovers
episodes.overview: Benja daydreams that one of the girls from the class will one day become his girlfriend. But his friend crushes on the same girl?

episodes.name: Felix's dangerous business
episodes.overview: Felix earns money by helping the 9th graders. But can Felix trust his business partner Noah, and is their business legal?

episodes.name: Threesome drama
episodes.overview: Nynne is a huge fan of Amalie's famous cousin, Anya. But when Anya visits the class, drama arises between Amalie and Nynne.

episodes.name: Agnes does not dare to say no
episodes.overview: Charlie challenges Agnes to be less boring. But does it end up going wrong - and does Agnes exceed her own limits?

episodes.name: Football over birthday
episodes.overview: Lotus has to play an important match on her birthday and will not celebrate. Clara doesn't understand how football can be so important?

episodes.name: The first kiss
episodes.overview: Hugo lies about having kissed a lot of girls. But maybe he can kiss someone from the class? Does he have a chance with Benedikte?

episodes.name: Secrets in the basement
episodes.overview: Bjarke, Agnes and Benja find an old box with notes. Can they solve the mystery and find out who left the box?

episodes.name: Embarrassed Clara
episodes.overview: Clara wants to hang out more with Lotus and arranges for them to appear on the party committee together. But will Clara end up embarrassing Lotus?

episodes.name: Smashing sister's shoes with dog shit
episodes.overview: Benedikte finds herself in a chaos of lies when she makes the mistake of "borrowing" her sister's shoes. Will she be discovered?

episodes.name: Benja's dilemma
episodes.overview: Benja suddenly gets the chance to get closer to Lotus. But will he have to choose between Lotus and best friend Agnes?

episodes.name: A poor family
episodes.overview: Møller discovers that Lucca's family does not have much money. He tries to convince the class that they must help. But can they?

episodes.name: Eigil's extreme treatment
episodes.overview: Eigil wants a six-pack, but it's difficult when Noah has baked Eigil's favorite cake for class. Will Eigil ever get a six pack?

episodes.name: Cute Nynne has had enough
episodes.overview: Nynne is tired of the other girls not taking her seriously just because she is small and short. But is her revenge too harsh?

episodes.name: Tobi in trouble
episodes.overview: Tobi discovers that MK has sinister plans for the school party. Can he tell the class, or will MK silence him?

episodes.name: Can the school party be saved?
episodes.overview: Will this year's school party be cancelled? Or can Lotus and Tobi manage to save the school party and the money MK has taken from the class?

episodes.name: Snap or sleep?
episodes.overview: Benedikte would like to join Clara and Lotus' group chat on Snap so they can become friends. But can she live up to their demands?

episodes.name: Tobi cheats on Felix
episodes.overview: Tobi and Felix agree that they will complete a challenge together. But can Tobi do it? Or is it ok to cheat on your friend?

episodes.name: Amalie's terrible nightmare
episodes.overview: Every night, Amalie has nightmares about the climate. How is she going to save the world from falling apart? Can Selma De Montgomery help?

episodes.name: The bicycle thief
episodes.overview: Bjarke can't find his bike. Has it been stolen at school? Agnes and Bjarke go together in search of the bicycle thief!

episodes.name: The wrong thief?
episodes.overview: Tobi is accused of being the bicycle thief. Will he be expelled? Does Bjarke have a guilty conscience?

episodes.name: Lotus' secret crush
episodes.overview: Lotus crushes on a guy, but are her feelings reciprocated? Clara helps Lotus write a flirtatious message - will he respond?

episodes.name: Trapped! - Part 1
episodes.overview: Benja and Bjarke have to fire it off for DKK 1,000 at home alone for the whole autumn holiday, but Møller gets them into some huge trouble!

episodes.name: Trapped! - Part 2
episodes.overview: Benja, Møller and Bjarke are not only locked up at school - they also discover a hidden secret in the girls' dressing.

episodes.name: Trapped! - Part 3
episodes.overview: Benja, Møller and Bjarke are threatened to take their pants down on the school roof while the big boys film them. Does the video end with Anders Hemmingsen?

episodes.name: Feelings for someone from 9th grade
episodes.overview: Lotus wants to score B from 9th grade. But he's sending her some mixed signals - is he interested, or is he just a player?

episodes.name: Clutter in love
episodes.overview: Benja is in love with a girl from the class. Is she interested in him too? Or are there obstacles to love?

episodes.name: Is Møller a scarecrow
episodes.overview: Charlie persuades Møller that they should play Spirit in the Glass. The mission is to scare him for life - will it work?

episodes.name: Nynne's competitor
episodes.overview: Nynne gets angry when Eske challenges her status as the creative genius of the class. Does she take revenge?

episodes.name: The strict teacher
episodes.overview: Stephanie and Amalie don't understand why Michael is suddenly angry and strict with the class. Maybe there is something wrong?

episodes.name: A new flirt?
episodes.overview: Bjarke has some bad luck. But what happens when he meets his partner?

episodes.name: Bjarke's dance partner
episodes.overview: Bjarke makes an agreement with Olga to dance together at the school party. But would he really rather dance with someone else?

episodes.name: Møller's old father... or grandfather?
episodes.overview: Møller lies to Felix, who teases him that Møller's father is old. But will he be caught in the lie - and can it hurt someone?

episodes.name: Rebellion against the headmaster!
episodes.overview: Charlie decides to make the class go against MK's unreasonable rules, of which there are more and more. Will it succeed?

episodes.name: Stronger than the big boys
episodes.overview: Eigil wants to be part of the class' cool boy group. But will they only be friends with him because he has big muscles?

episodes.name: The dream lunch package
episodes.overview: Casper Drømme shows up at school and rates Hjalmer and Hannibal's lunch packages. But is Hjalmer cheating because he is embarrassed by his food?

episodes.name: Crop tops prohibited!
episodes.overview: MK forbids crop tops at school. Stephanie decides that everyone should wear crop tops in protest! But does Amalie feel pressured?

episodes.name: Benjamin's deceit
episodes.overview: Lotus thinks she and B are making a deal to dance together at the prom. But when will Benja be discovered?

episodes.name: Drama on the dance floor
episodes.overview: At the school party, Benja will have to tell Lotus that he has been pretending to be B. How will that go?

episodes.name: School party smashed
episodes.overview: Agnes is without a partner for the dance competition and feels alone again. Will she discover something sinister as she wants to leave the party?

episodes.name: Everyone hates Agnes
episodes.overview: The holidays are over and everyone is back in class after the dramatic school party. Everyone - except Tobi. Has Agnes got him expelled?

episodes.name: Is Tobi banished forever?
episodes.overview: Agnes tries to convince the class to fight MK. So maybe they can get Tobi back? But what does teacher Michael say about that plan?

episodes.name: Can Carlo score the substitute?
episodes.overview: The class gets a new substitute. Is she flirting with Carlo? How do you score the substitute?

episodes.name: Tobi's last chance
episodes.overview: Clara wants to know why Tobi stole the money from the school party. Why can't she know the truth?

episodes.name: What is Eigil hiding?
episodes.overview: Noah misses Eigil and wishes they hung out like before, when the classes were combined. But why is Eigil lying to Noah?

episodes.name: In love or confused?
episodes.overview: Bjarke and B get closer to each other. But is Ruben ruining their relationship with his hateful and vicious comments?

episodes.name: Noah is punished
episodes.overview: Noah will do anything to get more time with Eigil. Does he regret it when he gets Ruben on his neck?

episodes.name: Reveals big secret
episodes.overview: Tobi and Agnes have dukejjans together. But Tobi panics when they get locked in the classroom. Does he tell Agnes why?

episodes.name: Heartbreaker
episodes.overview: Benja has doubts: does he still have a crush on Lotus? Is he more into Siri? Maybe he can find out by kissing Lotus?

episodes.name: Jealousy drama
episodes.overview: Clara is afraid that Tobi will break up and she tries to save the relationship. But will she end up making everything much worse?

episodes.name: Felix is sexist
episodes.overview: Benedikte and Siri challenge Felix's old-fashioned view of girls and women. Is he learning a lesson or is he lost?

episodes.name: Is Benja a huge pleaser?
episodes.overview: Can Benja figure out how to tell his friends what he really thinks? Or does he always just do as they say?

episodes.name: Parents argue all the time
episodes.overview: Eigil's parents argue and shout at each other a lot at home. It really doesn't feel cool, but who does Eigil dare to confide in?

episodes.name: Mission less meat
episodes.overview: Amalie and Steph disagree about how they should fight for the climate. Does meat-free week ever succeed?

episodes.name: Tobi's double life
episodes.overview: Agnes is annoyed with Tobi because he is always lazy at school. But at Tobi's house, he is the adult and takes care of... everything himself.

episodes.name: Smells musty
episodes.overview: Carlo wants to use deodorant, just like the other boys in the class.

episodes.name: Hugo's sense of humor is hilarious
episodes.overview: Hugo wants to be the funniest in the class. But is it even cool to make fun of others?

episodes.name: Avoid bathing after sports
episodes.overview: Eigil has a hard time with his body and prefers to avoid bathing with the other boys. Perhaps he is not alone in feeling this way?

episodes.name: The world's worst Valentine's Day
episodes.overview: Clara plans a lovely Valentine's Day for the class and hopes to get Tobi in a romantic mood. Will it end in chaos rather than kisses?

episodes.name: Anastasia from Ukraine
episodes.overview: Lotus will welcome the new girl in the class, Anastasia, who has escaped from Ukraine. Does Anastasia already know someone from the class?

episodes.name: Embarrassing to play
episodes.overview: Møller and Bille always dress up as Aase and Inge for Mardi Gras. This year maybe they have become too old to play old ladies?

episodes.name: Nynne does not want to fail
episodes.overview: Lucca and Nynne must present together, but Lucca does not take the task seriously. Does Nynne get uncomfortable and nervous?

episodes.name: Is Amalie truant?
episodes.overview: Why isn't Amalie at school? Is she truant? Or is there someone in the class who is bothering her?

episodes.name: Too expensive birthday
episodes.overview: Tobi's sister is turning eight, and he has organized a huge birthday party for her. How did Tobi pay for it all?

episodes.name: Tobi's taboo
episodes.overview: Agnes tries to get Tobi to talk to an adult about the excessive responsibility he has at home. Does he need help?

episodes.name: Steph on the shit
episodes.overview: It's impossible for Steph to shit with the boys around. Can she create a shitstorm and get the gender-neutral toilets shut down?

episodes.name: Have to choose between mother and father
episodes.overview: Eigil's parents have divorced, forcing him to choose between them. Can he do it without upsetting either of them or himself?

episodes.name: Møller's talent for drama
episodes.overview: Møller claims that he has a great acting career behind him. Does he get laughed at when the class has to perform a play?

episodes.name: Benedikte is under pressure
episodes.overview: Hugo and Benedikte have great fun together. But Hugo does one thing that annoys Benedikte to no end. Dare she tell him?

episodes.name: Noah's disgusting packed lunch
episodes.overview: Felix fears that Noah and Tobi will become friends. So Felix downplays Noah's packed lunch to keep Tobi as his friend. Does Noah get enough of it?

episodes.name: A true friend
episodes.overview: Bjarke's birthday is on the same day that Agnes is offered a huge opportunity. Can she manage both? Or is she ditching her friend?

episodes.name: Staying overnight at school divides the class
episodes.overview: The class is quickly divided into girl and boy groups, as they have to spend the night at the school. Where does Lucca belong?

episodes.name: Birthday bash
episodes.overview: Felix is the standard bearer of a new tradition: You get beaten on your birthday. However, Noah tries to dodge. Are the bitches only getting worse?

episodes.name: Møller's disability
episodes.overview: Møller can't stand sports and lies out of it by faking a disability. Has he gone too far with his lies?

episodes.name: Bjarke's famous pranks
episodes.overview: Bjarke wants to be big on YouTube, where he is successful with his pranks. Does he destroy the friendship with Benja in his pursuit of likes?

episodes.name: Bjarke's famous pranks go horribly wrong
episodes.overview: Bjarke feels like the king of the class, and his agent demands even more wicked pranks. But who is the agent really?

episodes.name: On scout's honor
episodes.overview: Once Møller, Bille and Noah went scouting together. But now they dare not continue for fear that Ruben will beat them - or what?

episodes.name: Clara's nail salon
episodes.overview: Clara is very successful in doing nails on the girls in frikva. But does Tobi get nervous that Clara might want to do nails forever?

episodes.name: Eva has no future
episodes.overview: Nynne pushes Eva to find out what she wants when she grows up. Will Eva end up being laughed at?

episodes.name: Felix's fake holiday
episodes.overview: Felix comes home from a great family vacation to the Bahamas. Or... did he?

episodes.name: Faith, horoscopes and love
episodes.overview: Nynne loves astrology and reads in Amalie's horoscope that she must open her heart. But does Amalie already have a crush on someone from the class?

episodes.name: Agnes believes in life in space
episodes.overview: Bjarke and Benja are tired of Agnes always wanting to decide everything. But how does she manage alone?

episodes.name: Religion vs. rebel
episodes.overview: Eva is very concerned about living the ten commandments of the Bible, but Lucca wants to teach her to relax a little more. Did it succeed?

episodes.name: Clara is a wannabe
episodes.overview: Clara wants to hang out more with Tobi and Lotus. How does she join their group without being a wannabe?

episodes.name: The anonymous letter
episodes.overview: Nynne and Charlie find a depressing letter in class. They must help the person who wrote the letter! But who could it be?

episodes.name: Dirty tricks
episodes.overview: Lotus and Eva are both good at soccer and become captains of their respective teams. How far will they go when they play against each other?

episodes.name: Who stole?
episodes.overview: Benedikte and Charlie are envious of the necklace Eva got from her grandmother. But suddenly the necklace is gone! Who stole it?

episodes.name: Why is Clara upset?
episodes.overview: Tobi is confused as to why Clara is upset and avoiding him. Has she been exposed to something unpleasant?

episodes.name: Does Carlo dare to go against Felix?
episodes.overview: Felix rides Charlie and Carlo is tired of just watching. But what happens if Carlo goes against Felix? Does he dare?

episodes.name: Noah and Felix on the warpath
episodes.overview: Noah fears that the war in Ukraine will come to Denmark. Felix decides to shock him with a prank. Does it backfire?

episodes.name: Benedikte is ditched
episodes.overview: Eske has become mega popular among the girls in the class and neglects his BFF, Benedikte. They never hang out anymore. Does she take revenge?

episodes.name: Secrets with Anna Munch
episodes.overview: Will Nynne tell about Charlie's biggest and deepest secret? Does Charlie counterattack? And why does Siri get so angry at Nynne?

episodes.name: Møller's adventurous kiss
episodes.overview: The class must perform Klods Hans. Møller is sure that he will get the leading role and a kiss from the king's daughter. But everything is not so easy...

episodes.name: Møller's adventurous kiss - Part 2
episodes.overview: Moller is desperate! How is he going to make sure that he and not Felix is allowed to kiss Charlie?

episodes.name: Amalie drops Steph
episodes.overview: Amalie doesn't show up as Steph prepares a long-awaited demo. Where is Amalie at? Why is she ditching Steph?

episodes.name: The gossip chat reveals the crush
episodes.overview: Bille finds a declaration of love for Siri and becomes obsessed with revealing the sender in the gossip chat. Who has a crush on Siri?

episodes.name: Comedy dreams
episodes.overview: Hugo gives Lucca the best birthday in the world and invites her to an open mic with Eva Jin. But what happens when Lucca takes the stage?

episodes.name: Does Steph have an eating disorder?
episodes.overview: Benedikte discovers that Steph is not eating anything and is constantly working out and practicing her cheerleading routine. Is Steph sick?

episodes.name: Noah's poop exercise day
episodes.overview: Exercise day is a blast as always, until Sophie asks Noah for help in making yoga camp. But who wants to ruin Noah's crush?

episodes.name: Freestyle Felix
episodes.overview: Can Felix's popular rap skills help Steph get noticed?

episodes.name: Møller aka Messi
episodes.overview: Tobi and the rest of the football team are one man down, so they will have to recruit Møller. Does he surprise on the pitch?

episodes.name: You snuff, you lose
episodes.overview: Felix wants to be bros with Simon and Emil from the 9th and promises to get them snuff. But how? Does he use Møller to steal?

episodes.name: Ultra fake Ultra New
episodes.overview: The class is visited by Inge from Ultra New. Agnes sees a huge chance to realize her dream. Will Benja and Bjarke get in the way?

episodes.name: Charlie is growing up
episodes.overview: Everything has suddenly changed for Charlie, and she can no longer play childish games with Nynne. Or is it just something she thinks?

episodes.name: Girlfriend or cash?
episodes.overview: Finally, Tobi has got a job and is earning his own money. But is the money more important than his relationship with Clara?

episodes.name: Clara breaks up
episodes.overview: Clara is happy that Tobi has finally shared his big secret with her. But is that enough for them to remain lovers?

episodes.name: Tivoli trip without Tobi?
episodes.overview: The class's new tradition will be a joint trip to Tivoli. But Tobi doesn't have the money for that. Is he the only one who can't afford it?

episodes.name: The death list
episodes.overview: Simon and Emil get Benja into a huge predicament, and Bjarke feels betrayed by his best friend. Can Bjarke forgive Benja?

episodes.name: Broken up forever? Part 1
episodes.overview: On the last day before the holidays, Agnes finds an overview of the old classes in the lecture hall. Should the class be split in two again?

episodes.name: Broken up forever? Part 2
episodes.overview: Bad atmosphere in the class! The door is locked, the key is gone, and everyone is locked inside. Or are they? Who is hiding the key - and why?

episodes.name: New Year, New Problems (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Unpleasant surprises await when the class returns from summer vacation. Will everything be changed forever?

episodes.name: What has Valdemar done? (part 2)
episodes.overview: The new boy in the class, Valdemar, has a dark past. But when Cleo wants to expose him, she gets a shock!

episodes.name: Cleo's Big Mistake (Part 3)
episodes.overview: Cleo tries to fix the bad situation she herself has created with misunderstandings and untruths. But is it too late?

episodes.name: Patrick's first day
episodes.overview: Patrick makes his entrance, and the class has to get used to new times. Pil and Lea in particular are dissatisfied. Can they do anything?

episodes.name: Cringe little sister
episodes.overview: Karl-Emil feels left out in class. And his little sister, Alberte, only makes it worse. What does he have to do to fit in?

episodes.name: Someone like Esther
episodes.overview: Esther is not like everyone else in the class. But who will stand up for Esther when Erika makes fun of her?

episodes.name: Naja Münster's revenge
episodes.overview: Naja Münster has to attend the class for one week, but things start badly between Naja and Erika. How does Naja get revenge?

episodes.name: Police stop the party
episodes.overview: Frans has planned a blast of a party to become popular in the class. But what happens when the police interrupt his plans?

episodes.name: Naja Münster is a substitute
episodes.overview: When Patrick doesn't show up for class, the class decides that Naja will be a substitute. But it doesn't go at all as Naja had planned...

episodes.name: Prank goes wrong
episodes.overview: Topper thinks that Holger and Jones are a bit childish. But things go awry when he tries to make friends with the big boys.

episodes.name: The pact
episodes.overview: Amira is challenged in S, P or K and must kiss Karl-Emil. But does she want to? Are they more than just friends?

episodes.name: Does Bloody Mary exist?
episodes.overview: Esther doesn't believe in the Bloody Mary myth. Can Frans and Freja convince her that something - or someone - is haunting the school?

episodes.name: Frenemies
episodes.overview: Bjørk and Erika were once good friends. They are no longer. But what actually happened? And why does Bjørk want revenge?

episodes.name: The drama queen of the class
episodes.overview: Bjørk and Erika have worn the same shirt for this year's class photo. But Erika creates drama around it. Will she get her way?

episodes.name: Noia AI
episodes.overview: Topper and Jones are lazy about a presentation. But is AI saving them?

episodes.name: Cleo Cheats (Part 1)
episodes.overview: The class must have grades in a French test. Cleo wants 12, but can she get it without cheating?

episodes.name: Cleo Cheats (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Cleo has a bad conscience towards Billy and hangs out with Valdemar instead. Is a new friendship emerging - or more?

episodes.name: Valdemar vs. Billy
episodes.overview: Cleo is friends with both Billy and Valdemar, but can you be 3 people in a friendship? How many guys can there be room for in Cleo's life?

episodes.name: Who is vaping? (part 1)
episodes.overview: A puff bar has been found on the school grounds. Who could think of vaping? And why does everyone think it's Maxi?

episodes.name: Who is vaping? (part 2)
episodes.overview: Mikkel and Lukas pressure Maxi and Isso. How can they avoid getting beaten up and at the same time clear Maxi's name?

episodes.name: Birthday haul
episodes.overview: Laura has a birthday and loves to make the most of it. But what happens when everyone in the class seems to have forgotten the day?

episodes.name: Dicte's diary (part 1)
episodes.overview: Dicte feels left out because Uma and Erika are flirting with the boys from the class above. Will she end up lying about having a boyfriend?

episodes.name: Dicte's diary (part 2)
episodes.overview: Felix has exposed Dicte's lie. How do Uma and Erika feel about their friend lying to them? Can they forgive Dicte?

episodes.name: An artificial friend
episodes.overview: Selma begins to doubt how good a friend Pil is. But is AI a true friend?

episodes.name: Just BFFs?
episodes.overview: Valdemar discovers that Cleo and Billy send each other a lot of hearts. Are they just friends or is there more going on between them?

episodes.name: A toxic friendship (part 1)
episodes.overview: Karl-Emil starts hanging out with Mikkel and Lukas. Why does he end up in a toxic friendship? Does he ditch Amira and Bjørk?

episodes.name: A toxic friendship (part 2)
episodes.overview: The class is completely divided because of the videos Karl-Emil has shared. Can he even make it up again?

episodes.name: Secret Crush (Part 1)
episodes.overview: Esther hates snap. But what happens when Freja persuades her anyway? Who is the mysterious guy she starts chatting with?

episodes.name: Secret Crush (Part 2)
episodes.overview: Esther has sent a selfie to someone she doesn't know on snap. Does he go to her class?

episodes.name: Secret Crush (Part 3)
episodes.overview: Why does Esther think it is Topper she has been chatting with? When will Valdemar reveal himself before it's too late?

episodes.name: The school's scary ghosts
episodes.overview: Topper is fascinated by a spooky tale of scary things that once happened at school... until it gets really scary!

episodes.name: Uma's untruths
episodes.overview: Erika and Dicte do not want to work with Uma. But what happens when Uma finds a Russian TikTok profile with 150,000 likes?

episodes.name: Afraid of conflict
episodes.overview: Amira finds it difficult to speak up and ends up never deciding anything. Can she learn to believe in herself a little more?

episodes.name: Pil's match
